text:
When attempting to parse valid Excel formula SUM(fenia fenia3) with apache.poi.ss.formula.FormulaParser.parse, it throws exception:

org.apache.poi.ss.formula.FormulaParseException: Parse error near char 10 'f' in specified formula 'SUM(fenia fenia3)'. Expected ',' or ')'

fenia and fenia3 in the formula are defined named ranges
creator: e.aivaloglou@tudelft.nl
